    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# account-transactions model tracks financial transaction records\n\n`powerhouse/account-transactions` (10 ops) records individual financial transactions. Part of the Finance & Billing domain alongside [[accounts model defines the chart of accounts structure]], [[billing-statement model captures periodic billing summaries]], and [[payment-terms model defines payment conditions and schedules]].\n\n## Position in Ecosystem\n\nSits in the Finance & Billing zone. Likely referenced by billing statements and invoices when itemizing charges.\n\n## Cross-Model References\n\n- Transactions reference accounts from the Accounts model\n- BillingStatement and Invoice models may aggregate transactions\n\nSince [[five models form a hierarchy from facet through template to offering to subscription to instance]], account-transactions operates downstream \u2014 recording the financial outcomes of subscription activity.\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[ecosystem map]]\n- [[object relations]]",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:26.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:26.000Z"
    }
  },
